1
00:00:24,333 --> 00:00:26,099
I've never taken you seriously.

2
00:00:26,099 --> 00:00:29,066
If I got a choice, I would never choose you.
I don't love you!

3
00:00:29,266 --> 00:00:31,133
Get out of my life!

4
00:00:45,566 --> 00:00:47,433
What are you doing here alone?

5
00:00:47,833 --> 00:00:49,153
Careful someone might snatch you.

6
00:00:50,133 --> 00:00:51,900
No response today...

7
00:00:59,466 --> 00:01:00,566
Why are you crying?

8
00:01:03,066 --> 00:01:05,966
Don't cry, dear. Wian's here.

9
00:01:07,433 --> 00:01:13,300
Who did this to you?
Tell me, I'll beat that guy.

10
00:01:16,199 --> 00:01:17,199
You don't have to.

11
00:01:18,433 --> 00:01:23,166
The one who did this to me, is myself.

12
00:01:23,166 --> 00:01:26,066
I found out something I shouldn't.

13
00:01:30,199 --> 00:01:31,699
You fought with Chok, didn't you?

14
00:01:33,433 --> 00:01:39,199
I've told you. That bastard is nothing
but an asshole.

15
00:01:42,333 --> 00:01:45,733
Just let it go
but let me ask you something.

16
00:01:46,466 --> 00:01:50,666
If you got a lover, will you cheat on them?

17
00:01:51,000 --> 00:01:55,599
And if you got bored of your partner,
will you sleep with other people?
